title: Misteur Valaire - Mr.Brian - ElectroJazzFunk de Sherbrooke!
description:
Music : Electro / Techno : MP3/192Kbps

This is the quintet's first masterpiece released in 2005. They are an electro/jazz/funk ensemble dedicated to innovation and beats, from Sherbrooke, Canada. 

Awesome to listen to at home, but even better in concert!
